  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Who is Abby</strong>  spanning <strong>eight chapters</strong> of relaxed gameplay. Tom’s sister,  has disappeared. Distrustful of the authorities Tom takes matters into his own hands. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Explore  Detailed Worlds</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > The world has been handcrafted to every minor detail. Every location you explore is a new piece of the puzzle, teeming with details  to be uncovered. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2614800/extras/b9964cfebe3a79de86508ad6da645c76.poster.avif?t=1766404876\" width=650 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2614800/extras/b9964cfebe3a79de86508ad6da645c76.webm?t=1766404876\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2614800/extras/b9964cfebe3a79de86508ad6da645c76.mp4?t=1766404876\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Engage the World Around You</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Interact with <strong>hundreds of objects</strong> that hold the key to unravelling the mystery. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2614800/extras/e5eb0e81bd073feacb717b774863753a.poster.avif?t=1766404876\" width=650 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2614800/extras/e5eb0e81bd073feacb717b774863753a.webm?t=1766404876\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2614800/extras/e5eb0e81bd073feacb717b774863753a.mp4?t=1766404876\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Become the Detective</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every corner hides a clue, and every clue could bring you one step closer to the truth. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2614800/extras/dce50b8ab353e130003c3fe4a1a96e30.poster.avif?t=1766404876\" width=600 height=166 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2614800/extras/dce50b8ab353e130003c3fe4a1a96e30.webm?t=1766404876\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2614800/extras/dce50b8ab353e130003c3fe4a1a96e30.mp4?t=1766404876\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Unveil the Truth Behind Abby’s Disappearance</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each discovery adds another piece to the puzzle, gradually revealing the story behind her disappearance. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2614800/extras/3bed367094a0817a5d3661f4714dc268.poster.avif?t=1766404876\" width=600 height=166 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2614800/extras/3bed367094a0817a5d3661f4714dc268.webm?t=1766404876\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2614800/extras/3bed367094a0817a5d3661f4714dc268.mp4?t=1766404876\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Overcome the Obstacles</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tom is desperate for answers, and nothing will stand in his way. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2614800/extras/76e8da3dcfa57fc364cb76dd68fd4783.poster.avif?t=1766404876\" width=600 height=166 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2614800/extras/76e8da3dcfa57fc364cb76dd68fd4783.webm?t=1766404876\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2614800/extras/76e8da3dcfa57fc364cb76dd68fd4783.mp4?t=1766404876\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key Features:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Narrative-Driven Exploration:</strong> A captivating blend of narrative and gameplay, merging the immersive storytelling of walking simulators with the hands-on witty interaction of classic point-and-click adventures. Navigate through a <strong>multi-chapter story</strong> that keeps you guessing until the very end. With each chapter offering 8+ hours of gameplay, the game delivers a substantial experience that keeps you engaged from start to finish.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Interactive Worlds:</strong> Every environment is richly detailed and interactive, filled with clues and secrets essential to unravelling the story. The game’s vast environments reward exploration, with each chapter introducing new locations and deeper mysteries to uncover. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Stunning Graphics and Sound:</strong> Powered by Unreal Engine 5, <strong>Who is Abby</strong> delivers cutting-edge visuals and immersive soundscapes, bringing Tom’s world to life with unparalleled realism. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Full Control Customization:</strong> Enjoy seamless support for both keyboard and controller. Customize your experience with remappable keys for keyboard and mouse, as well as an invertible Y-axis.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unlock the Bonus Museum Chapter:</strong> Venture deeper into the world of <strong>Who is Abby</strong> with a special museum chapter, packed with additional lore and secrets as you progress through the game. This bonus chapter adds even more depth to an already rich narrative experience. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Collectibles to Discover:</strong> Scattered throughout the world, collectibles await your discovery, each one adding another layer to the mystery. The extensive world is filled with secrets that encourage replayability, as you strive to uncover everything the game has to offer. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>It's time to uncover the truth.</strong></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Who is Abby</strong>  spanning <strong>eight chapters</strong> of relaxed gameplay. Tom’s sister,  has disappeared. Distrustful of the authorities Tom takes matters into his own hands. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Explore  Detailed Worlds</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > The world has been handcrafted to every minor detail. Every location you explore is a new piece of the puzzle, teeming with details  to be uncovered. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2614800/extras/b9964cfebe3a79de86508ad6da645c76.poster.avif?t=1766404876\" width=650 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2614800/extras/b9964cfebe3a79de86508ad6da645c76.webm?t=1766404876\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2614800/extras/b9964cfebe3a79de86508ad6da645c76.mp4?t=1766404876\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Engage the World Around You</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Interact with <strong>hundreds of objects</strong> that hold the key to unravelling the mystery. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2614800/extras/e5eb0e81bd073feacb717b774863753a.poster.avif?t=1766404876\" width=650 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2614800/extras/e5eb0e81bd073feacb717b774863753a.webm?t=1766404876\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2614800/extras/e5eb0e81bd073feacb717b774863753a.mp4?t=1766404876\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Become the Detective</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every corner hides a clue, and every clue could bring you one step closer to the truth. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2614800/extras/dce50b8ab353e130003c3fe4a1a96e30.poster.avif?t=1766404876\" width=600 height=166 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2614800/extras/dce50b8ab353e130003c3fe4a1a96e30.webm?t=1766404876\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2614800/extras/dce50b8ab353e130003c3fe4a1a96e30.mp4?t=1766404876\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Unveil the Truth Behind Abby’s Disappearance</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each discovery adds another piece to the puzzle, gradually revealing the story behind her disappearance. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2614800/extras/3bed367094a0817a5d3661f4714dc268.poster.avif?t=1766404876\" width=600 height=166 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2614800/extras/3bed367094a0817a5d3661f4714dc268.webm?t=1766404876\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2614800/extras/3bed367094a0817a5d3661f4714dc268.mp4?t=1766404876\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Overcome the Obstacles</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tom is desperate for answers, and nothing will stand in his way. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2614800/extras/76e8da3dcfa57fc364cb76dd68fd4783.poster.avif?t=1766404876\" width=600 height=166 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2614800/extras/76e8da3dcfa57fc364cb76dd68fd4783.webm?t=1766404876\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2614800/extras/76e8da3dcfa57fc364cb76dd68fd4783.mp4?t=1766404876\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key Features:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>Narrative-Driven Exploration:</strong> A captivating blend of narrative and gameplay, merging the immersive storytelling of walking simulators with the hands-on witty interaction of classic point-and-click adventures. Navigate through a <strong>multi-chapter story</strong> that keeps you guessing until the very end. With each chapter offering 8+ hours of gameplay, the game delivers a substantial experience that keeps you engaged from start to finish.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Interactive Worlds:</strong> Every environment is richly detailed and interactive, filled with clues and secrets essential to unravelling the story. The game’s vast environments reward exploration, with each chapter introducing new locations and deeper mysteries to uncover. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Stunning Graphics and Sound:</strong> Powered by Unreal Engine 5, <strong>Who is Abby</strong> delivers cutting-edge visuals and immersive soundscapes, bringing Tom’s world to life with unparalleled realism. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Full Control Customization:</strong> Enjoy seamless support for both keyboard and controller. Customize your experience with remappable keys for keyboard and mouse, as well as an invertible Y-axis.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Unlock the Bonus Museum Chapter:</strong> Venture deeper into the world of <strong>Who is Abby</strong> with a special museum chapter, packed with additional lore and secrets as you progress through the game. This bonus chapter adds even more depth to an already rich narrative experience. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Collectibles to Discover:</strong> Scattered throughout the world, collectibles await your discovery, each one adding another layer to the mystery. The extensive world is filled with secrets that encourage replayability, as you strive to uncover everything the game has to offer. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>It's time to uncover the truth.</strong></p>",
